    # "I drive over and pick Dana up. Then we go out to The Grotto together."
    "Conduzco hasta allí y recojo a Dana. Luego salimos juntos a The Grotto."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:28
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_2095cc55:

    # cw "Wow. This place is amazing."
    cw "Vaya. Este lugar es increíble."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:29
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_2ba00ab3:

    # cw "I can't believe I get to go out here. It's so beautiful."
    cw "No me puedo creer que haya podido venir aquí. Es precioso."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:30
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_05526a72:

    # pc "You're beautiful, Dana. You deserve it."
    pc "Tú eres preciosa, Dana. Te lo mereces."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:31
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_9c4b6956:

    # cw "Thank you, [pcname]."
    cw "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:32
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_37c9d0bf:

    # "We walk in and the host leads us to our seats."
    "Entramos y el maître nos acompaña a nuestra mesa."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:38
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_80af549c:

    # cw "You can afford this? On what Mrs. Mills pays you?"
    cw "¿Te lo puedes permitir? ¿Con lo que te paga la Sra. Mills?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:39
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_0f30c499:

    # pc "Sure. I mean, not every day or anything, but occasionally. I don't have many bills."
    pc "Claro. Bueno, no todos los días ni nada por el estilo, pero de vez en cuando. No tengo muchos gastos."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:40
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_a4bd3f4d:

    # pc "Don't worry about it though, Dana. I want you to have a great night."
    pc "Pero no te preocupes por eso, Dana. Quiero que pases una noche estupenda."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:42
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_617347d3:

    # cw "I already am. This is incredible."
    cw "Ya lo estoy haciendo. Esto es increíble."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:43
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_ecd9ab22:

    # "The server takes our orders and we chat for a while."
    "El camarero toma nota y charlamos un rato."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:46
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_ac38448c:

    # "Then we eat and chat some more."
    "Luego comemos y seguimos charlando."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:52
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_94d3f64e:

    # "Then we get up and dance a bit to the soft music."
    "Después nos levantamos y bailamos un poco al son de la música suave."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:54
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_d0b4cddc:

    # cw "You're so amazing. This is the best date I've ever been on."
    cw "Eres increíble. Esta es la mejor cita que he tenido nunca."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:55
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_1ece43ad:

    # cw "I couldn't want anything more."
    cw "No podría pedir nada más."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:56
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_f6634f6b:

    # pc "Anything to make you happy, Dana. That's all I want."
    pc "Cualquier cosa que te haga feliz, Dana. Eso es todo lo que quiero."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:60
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_93db9284:

    # cw "You do make me happy, [pcname]."
    cw "Me haces feliz, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:61
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_8b92acc5:

    # cw "I'm so very happy."
    cw "Estoy muy feliz."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:69
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_c8c4e655:

    # cw "I know a way you can make me even happier though."
    cw "Aunque sé de una forma en la que puedes hacerme aún más feliz."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:70
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:71
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_9a5a9a70:

    # cw "Are you ready to take me home?"
    cw "¿Estás listo para llevarme a casa?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:72
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_69a64407:

    # pc "Yes, I think we should."
    pc "Sí, creo que deberíamos."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:76
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_4097bbec:

    # "Fifteen minutes later we're in her bedroom and she's naked on the bed, practically begging me to ravage her."
    "Quince minutos más tarde estamos en su dormitorio y ella está desnuda en la cama, prácticamente suplicándome que la posea."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:80
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_ff3293a2:

    # cw "Do you want to continue this back at my place?"
    cw "¿Quieres continuar esto en mi casa?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:83
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_92e63c5d:

    # cw "Great. Let's go. I can't wait to get my mouth on you."
    cw "Genial. Vamos. Estoy deseando meterte en la boca."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:87
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_4097bbec_1:

    # "Fifteen minutes later we're in her bedroom and she's naked on the bed, practically begging me to ravage her."
    "Quince minutos más tarde estamos en su dormitorio y ella está desnuda en la cama, prácticamente suplicándome que la devore."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:91
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_627e2bde:

    # cw "Oh, alright."
    cw "Oh, vale."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:92
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_0128787c:

    # cw "It was still an incredible date. Thank you."
    cw "Aún así ha sido una cita increíble. Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaDates/danagrottodate.rpy:95
translate spanish danagrottostartdate_e8cbe586:

    # "I drive Dana home and we say our goodbyes, then she goes inside and I drive away to continue my night."
    "Llevo a Dana a casa y nos despedimos; luego ella entra y yo me marcho para seguir con mi noche."

